President Muhammadu Buhari on Monday night transmitted the list of Ministerial nominee to the Senate for screening. The list which was sent via executive communication has been read on the floor of the Senate. The list contains 42 names 1. Ikechukwu Ogar 2. Mohammed Musa Bello 3. Godswill Akpabio 4. Chris Ngige 5. Adamu Adamu 6. Maryam Katagun 7. Timipre Sylva 8. George Akume 9. Mustapha Baba Shehuri 10. Festus Keyamo 11. Clement Ike 12. Richard Adeniyi
Adebayo 13. Geoffrey Onyeama 14. Ali Pantami 15. Emeka Nwajubo 16. Suleiman Adamu 17. Zainab Ahamed
Muhammad 18. Mahmood
Sabo Nano 19. Hadi Sirika 20. Abubakar Malami 21. Rahmatu Tijjani 22.Lai Mohammed 23. Olorunnibe Mamora 24. Babatunde Fashola 25. Mohammed H. Abdullahi 26. Zubair Dada 27.Tayo Alasoadura 28. Rauf Aregbesola 29. Sunday Dare 30.Paullen Talen 31. Rotimi Amaechi 32. Sale Mamman 33. Abubakar D. Aliyu 34. Sadiya Umar Faruk  Among others Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook 